  27,12,"Now put your hand through ňĻthe opening ofňļ your collar, it will come out ňĻshiningňļ white, unblemished.¬†ňĻThese are twoňļ of nine signs for Pharaoh and his people.¬†They have truly been a rebellious people.‚ÄĚ"
