  43,80,"Or do they think that We do not hear their ňĻevilňļ thoughts and secret talks? Yes ňĻWe doňļ! And Our messenger-angels are in their presence, recording ňĻit allňļ"
  43,81,"Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúIf the Most Compassionate ňĻreallyňļ had offspring, I would be the first worshipper.‚ÄĚ"
  43,82,"Glorified is the Lord of the heavens and the earth, the Lord of the Throne, far above what they claim"
  43,83,"So let them indulge ňĻin falsehoodňļ and amuse ňĻthemselvesňļ until they face their Day, which they have been warned of"
  43,84,"It is He Who is ňĻthe onlyňļ God in the heavens and ňĻthe onlyňļ God on the earth. For He is the All-Wise, All-Knowing"
  43,85,And Blessed is the One to Whom belongs the kingdom of the heavens and the earth and everything in between! With Him ňĻaloneňļ is the knowledge of the Hour. And to Him you will ňĻallňļ be returned
  43,86,"ňĻButňļ those ňĻobjects of worshipňļ they invoke besides Him have no power to intercede, except those who testify to the truth knowingly"
