  72,18,"The places of worship are ňĻonlyňļ for God, so do not invoke anyone besides Him"
  72,19,"Yet when the servant of God¬†stood up calling upon Him ňĻaloneňļ, the pagans almost swarmed over him"
  72,20,"Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúI call only upon my Lord, associating none with Him ňĻin worshipňļ.‚ÄĚ"
